# âš–ï¸ Ifâ€“Else 

```bash
num=10
if [ $num -gt 5 ]; then
  echo "Bigger than 5 "
else
  echo "Smaller or equal "
fi
```
![alt text](images/image-27.png)

ğŸ§¾ Common operators:

* `-eq` equal
* `-ne` not equal
* `-gt` greater
* `-lt` less

