# ğŸ” Loops 

ğŸ”¹ **For Loop**

```bash
for i in {1..3}
do
  echo "Round $i ğŸŒ€"
done
```

ğŸ”¹ **While Loop**

```bash
count=1
while [ $count -le 3 ]
do
  echo "Count = $count"
  ((count++))
done
```
![alt text](images/image-28.png)
