# ğŸ’¡ Command Line Arguments 

```bash
#!/bin/bash
echo "Script: $0"
echo "First: $1"
echo "Second: $2"
```

Run:

```bash
./test.sh apple banana
```

Output:

```
Script: ./test.sh
First: apple
Second: banana
```
![alt text](images/image-30.png)


