# ğŸğŸŒğŸ’ Arrays 

```bash
fruits=("apple" "banana" "cherry")
echo "First fruit: ${fruits[0]}"

for f in "${fruits[@]}"; do
  echo "Fruit: $f"
done
```
OUTPUT:


![alt text](images/image-31.png)

