# ğŸ“’ Cheat Sheet (Quick Recall)

| Feature | Syntax            | Example           |
| ------- | ----------------- | ----------------- |
| Print   | `echo`            | `echo "Hi"`       |
| Var     | `var=value`       | `x=10`            |
| Input   | `read var`        | `read name`       |
| If      | `if [ cond ]`     | `if [ $x -gt 5 ]` |
| For     | `for i in {1..5}` | `echo $i`         |
| While   | `while [ cond ]`  | `((count++))`     |

